# VCF/Plotein environment variables
#
# VITE_URL_API — optional override for the companion API base URL.
#
# By default the app talks to the companion API through the relative `/api`
# path. In development, Vite's dev-server proxy (see vite.config.js) forwards
# `/api/*` to the UNAM backend. In production, server/index.js does the same.
# Because the proxy handles routing (and bypasses the expired upstream TLS
# cert), this variable is OPTIONAL and normally left unset.
#
# Only set this if you need to point the app at a different API host without
# going through the proxy.
# VITE_URL_API=/api
